OL,4,Cput more than 250 people in danger
OL,6,FThe driver managed to move the crane
OL,7,Faway from the ship and over the
OL,8,Fdockside before it collapsed, with the
OL,9,Fjib landing on a cage of acetylene
OL,10,Fcylinders.
OL,12,FThere were approximately 258 workers
OL,13,Fon site at the time.
OL,15,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,16,Finvestigation found A&P Falmouth, a
OL,17,Fcompany with an address in Tyne and
OL,18,FWear, had failed to properly maintain
OL,19,Fthe crane.
