OL,6,FHSE inspector Melissa Lai-Hung said:
OL,7,F"This was a very serious incident and
OL,8,Fit is fortunate nobody was injured or
OL,9,Fkilled as a result of this
OL,10,Fcatastrophic failure at Falmouth Docks.
OL,12,F"We thoroughly investigated this
OL,13,Fincident and found that A&P Falmouth
OL,14,FLimited's system of maintenance was
OL,15,Fnot effective in preventing the
OL,16,Fcollapse of the crane.
